detail_desc: T-shirt in soft slub jersey made from a modal and cotton blend. Short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups and a rounded hem.
Sleeveless blouse in a crêpe weave with a stand-up collar, ties at the front, a yoke with a pleat at the back, and a rounded hem.

Shopper in grained imitation leather with two handles, a gold-coloured zip at the top and three inner compartments, one with a zip. Gold-coloured zips at the sides to adjust the size of the bag. Lined. Size 14x30.5x43 cm.
Jumper in a soft, fine cotton knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Boxy jacket in airy cotton twill with a collar, buttons down the front and a yoke at the back. Chest pockets with a pleat and button, gently dropped shoulders, buttoned cuffs and a drawstring at the hem. Unlined.
Round-necked, long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a print motif. Rounded and slightly longer at the back.
Long-sleeved top in cotton sweatshirt fabric with press-studs on one shoulder, lapped ribbing at the neckline and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Short-sleeved top in fast-drying, breathable functional fabric with a print motif at the top and at the front and back of the hem. The polyester content of the top is partly recycled.

Slim-fit jeans in different colours of washed, superstretch, flexible denim for maximum mobility. Adjustable, elasticated waist (in sizes 8-12Y), zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and narrow hems.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool with a square neckline and long puff sleeves. Wide ribbing at the cuffs and hem. The polyester content of the jumper is recycled.
Set with two long-sleeved tops and two pairs of trousers in soft, organic cotton jersey. Tops with lapped shoulders. Trousers with an elasticated drawstring waist and ribbed hems.
Two-strand necklace in different widths of metal chain. Adjustable length.
Imitation leather hi-tops with woven fabric details, a padded edge, hook and loop tabs at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.

Blouse in a crinkled viscose weave with a scalloped edge and crocheted lace trim around the neckline, and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Inset, crocheted lace trims at the front, long sleeves with elasticated cuffs, a seam at the waist and a flounced hem.
Straight-cut, short-sleeved shirt in a patterned cotton weave. Relaxed fit with a turn-down collar, classic front and rounded hem with slits in the sides.
Brazilian briefs in microfibre with laser-cut edges. Low waist, lined gusset and a high cut at the back.
Cardigan in a soft, textured cotton knit with a round neckline, buttons down the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Straight-cut dress in a viscose weave with a V-neck and pleat at the front, dropped shoulders and short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups. Unlined.
Jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with low dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Calf-length, pleated skirt in woven fabric with an elasticated waist. Lined.
Long-sleeved tops in soft jersey made from a modal and cotton blend.
Hat in a soft knit with a decorative pompom on top, ribbed hem and earflaps. Thermal fleece lining.

Shorts in fast-drying functional fabric designed to help keep you dry and cool while running. Elastication and a concealed drawstring at the waist, zipped side pockets and ventilating mesh at the crotch for increased ventilation. Legs with reflective details for increased visibility outdoors and a slit in one side of the hems. Soft jersey inner shorts.

Hoodie in printed sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend. Lined hood with an elastic drawstring, and a kangaroo pocket with a concealed zip. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a mid waist, medium coverage at the back and laser-cut, scalloped edges.
Straight-cut coat in soft imitation suede with a small stand-up collar, patch front pockets and a detachable tie belt at the waist. No fasteners.

Long-sleeved top in stretch cotton jersey with a V-neck, raw-edge neckline and open chest pocket. Muscle fit – a fit designed to showcase the physique. Narrow shoulders and tapered sleeves create a flattering silhouette.
Top in airy cotton jersey with a wide neckline and two flounces in woven fabric on the sleeves.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with dropped shoulders and slits in the sides with ties. Ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Sunglasses with metal frames and UV-protective, tinted lenses.
Off-the-shoulder playsuit in an airy viscose weave with adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps and elastication and a wide flounce at the top. Elasticated seam at the waist and side pockets.
Top in sweatshirt fabric with a lined, drawstring hood, kangaroo pocket and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Thin metal chain necklace with sparkly stones and flat pearly plastic pendants at the front. Adjustable length 43-51 cm.
Push-up bra in lace with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, and a lace detail and narrow hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Long earrings in plastic and metal with round pendants. Length 10.5 cm.
Calf-length jumpsuit in soft slub cotton jersey with concealed press-studs at the back of the neck, a flounce in a broderie anglaise weave over each shoulder, and an elasticated seam at the waist.
Jumper in a soft rib knit with a round neckline and low dropped shoulders.
Metal studs in various designs.
Fine-knit socks.
Long, wide rib-knit jumper in a soft mohair blend with wide ribbing around the neckline, dropped shoulders and long, wide sleeves.
Long-sleeved top in Sweatshirt fabric with print motifs and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Calf-length skirt in mesh with a high slit at the front and an overlocked hem. High waist with concealed elastication. Lined with a short jersey skirt.
Straight-cut shirt in a soft viscose weave with a collar, buttons down the front, long sleeves with narrow, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Elastic bracelet with a reflective print.
Short, boxy top in printed sweatshirt fabric with a stand-up collar, zip at the top and ribbing around the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Sleeveless V-neck dress in a patterned weave with gathers on the shoulders, buttons at the top, a smocked seam under the bust and concealed pockets in the side seams. Unlined.
Fully lined, waist-high bikini bottoms with high-cut legs and a high cut at the back.
Small, sturdy handbag in imitation leather with two handles and a zip at the top and a detachable metal chain shoulder strap. One inner compartment. Lined. Size 9x13x17.5 cm.

Set with a bodysuit and trousers in soft organic cotton jersey. Long-sleeved bodysuit with decorative buttons and a pocket at the top, and press-studs at the crotch and on the shoulders. Trousers with foldover ribbing at the waist, a fake fly and ribbed hems.
Tube scarf in a soft cable knit. Width 25 cm, circumference 55 cm.
Fitted, long-sleeved dress in velour with a V-neck, decorative knot detail with gathers at the waist and a seam at the back.

Padded bomber jacket in woven fabric with a sheen. Detachable hood in sweatshirt fabric with a print motif on the back, and a small, ribbed stand-up collar. Zip down the front, side pockets with a press-stud, gathered seams down the sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Lined.

Jumpsuit in woven fabric with wide, flounce-trimmed shoulder straps and a smocked bodice with elastication and a small frill trim at the top. Frill-trimmed seam at the waist and wide, straight legs. Unlined.
Sleeveless top in stretch jersey crêpe with a small, frill-trimmed stand-up collar and V-shaped opening with ties at the top.
Shorts in woven fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and a back pocket.

Short-sleeved shirt in a cotton weave with a turn-down collar and classic front. Yoke at the back, a chest pocket, and a rounded hem. Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently shaped waist to create a comfortable, tailored silhouette.

Ankle-length trousers in woven fabric with a high waist, extended waistband with a concealed hook-and-eye fastener and a zip fly. Side pockets, fake back pockets and straight legs that taper gently to the hem with creases.
Poncho in an airy crinkled weave containing glittery threads, that is open at the front and sides. Fringe trims.

Push-up bra in lace and mesh with underwired, moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Lace racer back, narrow adjustable shoulder straps, a wide mesh strap at the back and a metal fastener at the front.
Fitted cardigan in a soft, fine, rib-knit viscose blend with a collar and buttons down the front.
Rattle in a soft knit in the shape of a teddy bear. Polyester padding. Width approx. 9 cm. Length approx. 13 cm.
Non-wired push-up bra in microfibre with padded, moulded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening.

Straight-cut shirt in an airy cotton weave with a collar, buttons down the front and an open chest pocket. Yoke with a pleat at the back, long sleeves with wide, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Scarf in a soft, fine knit with fringes on the short sides. Size 45x190 cm.

Lightweight running jacket in windproof, water-repellent functional fabric with a zip down the front and zipped side pockets. Hood that can be rolled up and fastened into the back of the neck with a tab and press-stud, a loose yoke at the back and mesh back section. Drawstring hem and reflective details. Unlined.
Sports tights in fast-drying functional fabric with an elasticated waist. One patterned pair and one pair in a solid colour.

Knee-length dress in woven fabric with a draped neckline at the front and concealed zip at the back. Long sleeves and cuffs with covered buttons. Seam at the waist, a detachable fabric belt with metal D-rings and a gently flared skirt. Unlined.
Swim shorts in a patterned weave with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and a back pocket with a hook and loop fastening. Mesh inner shorts.
Short shorts in light sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets.

Jacket in corduroy with a faux shearling-lined collar, buttons down the front, flap chest pockets with a button and welt side pockets. Adjustable tab at the sides, and buttoned cuffs. Partly lined in faux shearling.

Shirt in soft leather with pointed lapels and concealed press-studs down the front. Rounded sleeves with volume that taper to the cuffs, a tapered waist with seams, a gentle flare to the hem and high slits in the sides. Lightly brushed inside.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a round neckline and a print motif.
Long-sleeved shirt in soft brushed twill with a small embroidered detail on the chest, buttoned cuffs and a contrasting colour on the inside of the collar stand and cuffs.
Long-sleeved tunic in jersey crêpe with a rounded hem.

Long-sleeved top in soft jersey and a pair of dungarees in organic cotton sweatshirt fabric. Dungarees with a kangaroo pocket, adjustable straps with a press-stud, and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Long nightshirt in soft cotton flannel with notch lapels, a chest pocket, buttons down the front, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
Jumper in a soft, fine cotton knit with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Trousers in a Tencel™ lyocell weave with a detachable tie belt, pleats and the top and a zip in the side. Side pockets, a fake welt back pocket and tapered legs.

Negligee in lace and mesh with an integral super push-up bra with underwired, thickly padded cups to maximise the bust and create a fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Hi tops with a lightly padded edge and tongue, and lacing at the front. Mesh linings and insoles and patterned soles.
